coderExample:
// This is a single-line comment
Console.WriteLine("This runs!"); // Comments can go at the end of a line too!

/* This is a multi-line comment.
   You can write as much as you want.
   The computer will ignore ALL of this! */

Console.WriteLine("This also runs!");

challenge.instructions:
Write a program that displays a simple ASCII art (like a smiley face), but ADD COMMENTS explaining each line!

For example:
// Top of the face
Console.WriteLine("  ^   ^  ");
// The mouth
Console.WriteLine("   ---   ");

challenge.starterCode:
// Create your ASCII art here!
// Remember to add comments explaining each part!

Console.WriteLine("Add your art here");

challenge.solutionCode:
// Top of the face - the eyes
Console.WriteLine("  ^   ^  ");

// The nose (simple dot)
Console.WriteLine("    .    ");

// The mouth (happy smile)
Console.WriteLine("   ---   ");
